      <title>哈德逊湾加入对冲基金行列，将投资者现金锁定更长时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/hudson-bay-joins-hedge-funds-locking-up-investor-cash-for-longer</link>
